"shipping\":{\"item_is_shippable\":false,\"user_allows_shipping\":false,\"cost_configuration_id\":null},\"supports_shipping\":false,\"brand\":\"Porsche\",\"model\":\"911\",\"year\":2002,\"version\":\"996 Carrera 4S Coupé 3.6 320 2p Tip.S\",\"km\":89000,\"gearbox\":\"automatic\",\"horsepower\":320.0,\"favorited\":false,\"creation_date\":\"2025-03-01T15:05:46.033+00:00\",\"modification_date\":\"2025-03-23T18:46:36.183+00:00\",\"is_top_profile\":false}},{\"id\":\"xzo29eyy7269\",\"type\":\"cars_search_cars\",\"content\":{\"id\":\"xzo29eyy7269\",\"title\":\"Porsche 911 Carrera 4s MANUAL \",\"storytelling\":\"C27 NACIONAL. Motor nuevo en Porsche en garantia a los 171.000km por rotura de IMS. Mantenimientos sellados en la casa hasta los 240.000km. Embrague nuevo con bimasa a los 220.000km en Porsche. Neumaticos nuevos. Cambio manual. Navegador. Asientos electricos. Xenon. 2 llaves.\\nEn el precio se entrega transferido con factura con IVA deducible\\nal 50%.\\nLo compré en 2014 y lo vendo porque apenas lo uso y me da pena verlo parado. \\n\\nCONFIGURACION del coche:\\nSalpicadero e Interiores en cuero\\nBatería grande de 80Ah\\n030 suspension -20mm\\n220 diff autoblocante al 40%\\nXcz short shifter\\nXRP 5mm spacers all wheels\\nXSA respaldos color coche\\nXSC reposacabezas grabados\\n\",\"distance\":1.0,\"images\":[{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/yc/__/c10420p1106789981/i5441179386.jpg?pictureSi