97, 325CV), año 2007. 87.573 Kms. 59.900€. \\nNACIONAL.TODAS LAS REVISIONES EN PORSCHE OFICIAL SEGUNDO PROPIETARIO. MUY CUIDADO.\\nEtiqueta ambiental C (verde). Color azul metalizado - Paquete interior en cuero marrón – Asientos con regulación eléctrica - Volante en cuero – Se entrega capota dura - Equipo de sonido con Bluetooth con Android-Auto,  Apple-CarPlay y teléfono (se entregada la radio original, no montada)- Parktronic trasero – Llantas de aleación 19 pulgadas con pinzas de freno rojas - Climatizador - Cambio manual (hay muy pocos) - Bi-xenon con lavafaros -  Logo Porsche en los asientos – Porsche Stability Management (PSM). ITV al día.\",\"distance\":11.0,\"images\":[{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230423.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"original_width\":0,\"original_height\":0},{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230445.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230445.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230445.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230445.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ia/4w/__/c10420p1105416223/i5429230445.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https