 CON TARJETA SIM\\n670 MODULO DE NAVEGACIÓN  PARA PCM\\n680 SISTEMA DE SONIDO BOSÉ\\nOtras opciones:\\nCortavientos abatible desmontable y plegable\\nAdaptador para Ipod\\nFunda original de interior con Logo Porsche\\nITV hasta julio 2026 todas pasadas sin ningún fallo\\nTratamientos cerámico aplicado hace unos meses para dos años, super cuidado pintura e interior impecable siempre en garaje vehículo nacional comprado en  Centro Porsche Madrid Oeste solo un propietario anterior.\\nTres llaves originales libros y todas las facturas disponibles desde el primer día \\n\\n\\n\",\"distance\":12.0,\"images\":[{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5280969397.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"original_width\":0,\"original_height\":0},{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/hn/ut/__/c10420p1067993948/i5233613354.jpg?pictur