HRONO.\\n- Suspensión PASM con chasis adaptativo y modo SPORT.\\n- Sistema de navegación profesional en PCM original.\\n- Llantas de 19 pulgadas con pinzas de freno en color rojo.\\n- Climatizador bi zona.\\n\\n-12 MESES DE GARANTÍA  \\n-ACEPTAMOS COCHE COMO PARTE DE PAGO\\n-ENTREGAMOS VEHÍCULO EN TODA ESPAÑA\\n-WE ALSO SPEAK ENGLISH / HABLAMOS INGLÉS\\n\\nSi necesita más información, no dude en contactarnos.\\nVisita nuestra web para conocer todo nuestro stock y nuestras redes sociales @carbrokerspain\\n* Este anuncio puede contener errores y NO ES VINCULANTE.\",\"distance\":17.0,\"images\":[{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487068976.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"original_width\":0,\"original_height\":0},{\"original\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"xsmall\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"small\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W320\",\"large\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W800\",\"medium\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W640\",\"xlarge\":\"https://cdn.wallapop.com/images/10420/ie/pz/__/c10420p1113118385/i5487069028.jpg?pictureSize=W800\